                    <bibl><ptr target="#cdl2020a"/>, p. <citedRange>189-191</citedRange></bibl>.
                    </p>
                    <p>For a general bibliography on the accounts of the damiergoi see <ref type="inscription" source="#IGCyr2">IGCyr011400</ref>.
