                            <expan><abbr><am><g type="drachma">𐅂</g></am></abbr><ex>δραχμᾶν</ex></expan> <num type="cardinal" value="2"><measure type="currency" unit="drachma"><g type="alphabetic">β</g></measure></num>. 
                    Τὸ  <w lemma="πᾶς">πάν</w>, τὰ <w lemma="ἱαρεῖον">ἱαρεῖα</w> <w lemma="θύω">ἐθύθη</w>·
